      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Appointed Non-Executive Director to the VMD in May 2014 and Chairs the Audit and Risk Committee. As a former Director at the National Audit Office and in other roles he has over 25 years’ experience helping to provide assurance to public sector bodies on their financial and operational performance. He is also a non-executive Director at the Wales Audit Office and Chair of their Audit and Risk Management Committee.</p>
</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_2556">
            <h1 id="non-executive-director-vmd">Non-Executive Director, VMD</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>David Chairs the VMD Audit and Risk Assurance Committee, a sub-committee of the VMD Management Board and is a member of the Management Board (MB). The VMD Audit and Risk Assurance Committee (ARAC) supports the Chief Executive as Accounting Officer and the MB in monitoring the corporate governance and control systems in the organisation. It will advise on internal and external audit matters, risk, control and governance in the organisation. The ARAC’s scope and responsibilities include risk management, internal control, governance, financial reporting and internal and external audit.</p>
</div>
            <div class="read-more">
